# AWS S3 — raw data sync
# Fill in real values in .env (never commit .env)
AWS_REGION=<REGION>
AWS_S3_BUCKET=<BUCKET>
AWS_S3_PREFIX=mongle-village

# Credentials: prefer `aws configure` profile or IAM role over hardcoding.
# Only set these if you can't use a profile:
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
# AWS_PROFILE=default


# OpenAI — for LLM/VLM/image generation in character_creation adapters
OPENAI_API_KEY=
